'''德克薩斯訴賓夕法尼亞等'''（[[美国最高法院|最高法院]]案卷号22O155）是德克萨斯州向美国最高法院提起的诉讼。其对[[2020年美国总统大选|2020年美国总统大选]]的结果，亦即預計[[祖·拜登|祖·拜登]]擊敗特朗普，獲得足夠選舉人團票數一事提出异议<ref>{{cite web|last=Blood|first=Michael R.|last2=Riccardi|first2=Nicholas|date= 2020-12-05|title=Biden officially secures enough electors to become president|url=https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-joe-biden-donald-trump-elections-electoral-college-3e0b852c3cfadf853b08aecbfc3569fa|deadurl=no|access-date= 2020-12-12|website=[[Associated_Press|AP News]]|archive-date= 2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208201209/https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-joe-biden-donald-trump-elections-electoral-college-3e0b852c3cfadf853b08aecbfc3569fa}}</ref>。

德克萨斯州检察长肯·帕克斯顿（Ken Paxton）于2020年12月8日提起诉讼，指控[[喬治亞州|乔治亚州]]，[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]，[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]和[[威斯康辛州|威斯康星州]]在选举前更改选举程序，从而违反了[[美国宪法|美国宪法]]。该诉讼要求在2020年12月14日[[美国选举人|美国选举人]]投票之前，暂时扣起这四个州的核证投票数。这起诉讼於约50起选举结果争议相關诉讼失败后提起，當中不少涉及選舉舞弊的指控。而這宗诉讼並沒有有關選舉舞弊的指控，反認為被告各州透過非立法行為者（即司法和行政部门）修改選舉相關法律，因此涉嫌違反宪法。

在德州提出诉讼申请的24小時內，特朗普、一百多名共和党众议员、十八名共和党州检察长提出动议，以支持該宗申請<ref>{{cite news|last=Gillman|first=Todd J.|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2020/12/09/trump-says-hell-join-texas-lawsuit-asking-supreme-court-to-block-62-biden-electors-from-four-states/|title=17 states, and Trump, join Texas request for Supreme Court to overturn Biden wins in four states|date=December 9, 2020-12-09|work=The Dallas Morning News|access-date=2020-12-10|archive-date= 2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209212932/https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2020/12/09/trump-says-hell-join-texas-lawsuit-asking-supreme-court-to-block-62-biden-electors-from-four-states/|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/08/us/politics/texas-files-an-audacious-suit-with-the-supreme-court-challenging-the-election-results.html|title=Texas files an audacious suit with the Supreme Court challenging the election results.|first=Adam|last=Liptak|date= 2020-12-08|work=The New York Times|access-date=2020-12-09|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209023641/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/08/us/politics/texas-files-an-audacious-suit-with-the-supreme-court-challenging-the-election-results.html|deadurl=no}}</ref>。特朗普稱其為「大案」<ref name=ct2>{{cite news|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/election-2020/ct-republicans-texas-supreme-court-election-lawsuit-20201211-gnoqqkepqbfwxiuoc3b5oqnjvy-story.html|title=Majority of Republican House members sign on to lawsuit asking Supreme Court to invalidate presidential election|last1=Merchant|first1=Nomaan|last2=Richer|first2=Alanna Durkin|work=Chicago Tribune|access-date=2020-12-11|archive-date= 2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211192310/https://www.chicagotribune.com/election-2020/ct-republicans-texas-supreme-court-election-lawsuit-20201211-gnoqqkepqbfwxiuoc3b5oqnjvy-story.html||deadurl=no}}</ref>。被告州份的总检察长連同20個州份、兩個領地、哥伦比亚特区提交了幾份简报<ref name="reuters 20201210">{{cite web | url = https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-usa-election-trump/states-respond-to-texas-bid-to-overturn-u-s-election-at-supreme-court-idINKBN28K30R | title = States assail 'bogus' Texas bid to overturn U.S. election at Supreme Court | first = Lawrence | last = Hurley | date = 2020-12-10 | accessdate = 2020-12-11 | publisher = Reuters | archive-date =  2020-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201210211505/https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-usa-election-trump/states-respond-to-texas-bid-to-overturn-u-s-election-at-supreme-court-idINKBN28K30R |deadurl=no}}</ref>，敦促法院拒绝受理此案，称其为「煽动性地滥用司法程序」<ref name = po0 >{{cite web | url = https://www.politico.com/news/2020/12/10/seditious-abuse-judicial-process-reject-texas-effort-election-joe-biden-win-444414 | title = 'Seditious abuse of the judicial process': States reject Texas effort to overturn Biden's election | first1 = Kyle | last1 = Cheney | first2 = Zach | last2 = Montellaro | date =  2020-12-10 | accessdate = 2020-12-10 | work = [[Politico|Politico]] | archive-date =2020-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201210212707/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/12/10/seditious-abuse-judicial-process-reject-texas-effort-election-joe-biden-win-444414 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。多名法律專家表示其不太可能成功，猶如「万福玛利亚传球」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.scotusblog.com/2020/12/texas-tries-hail-mary-to-block-election-outcome/ |title=Texas tries Hail Mary to block election outcome |work=SCOTUSblog |access-date= 2020-12-10 |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209234514/https://www.scotusblog.com/2020/12/texas-tries-hail-mary-to-block-election-outcome/|deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="market">{{cite news|last=Matthews|first=Chris|date= 2020-12-09|title=Trump places hopes in longshot Texas lawsuit, asking Supreme Court to overturn election results in 4 states|url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/trump-places-hopes-in-longshot-texas-lawsuit-asking-supreme-court-to-overturn-election-results-in-4-states-11607542582|work=Market Watch|access-date= 2020-12-09|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209193850/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/trump-places-hopes-in-longshot-texas-lawsuit-asking-supreme-court-to-overturn-election-results-in-4-states-11607542582|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="ad">{{cite web|last=Dershowitz|first=Alan|date=|title=The Dershow, December 9, 2020: Trump Team Hail Mary & Last Day to Save Brandon Bernard|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xXQr9LtkMTA|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210204400/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xXQr9LtkMTA|archive-date= 2020-12-10|access-date= 2020-12-09|via=YouTube}}</ref>。

最高法院于2020年12月11日頒佈命令，拒绝审理此案，理由是根据宪法第三条，德州没有资格对其他州的选举结果和程序提出异议<ref>{{Cite news|last=Liptak|first=Adam|date=2020-12-11|title=Supreme Court Rejects Texas Suit Seeking to Subvert Election|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/11/us/politics/supreme-court-election-texas.html|access-date=2020-12-12|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=December 11, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211234955/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/11/us/politics/supreme-court-election-texas.html|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web|title=Order in Pending Case|url=https://www.supremecourt.gov/orders/courtorders/121120zr_p860.pdf|date=2020-12-11|publisher=Supreme Court of the United States|access-date=2020-12-11|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211234004/https://www.supremecourt.gov/orders/courtorders/121120zr_p860.pdf|deadurl=no }}</ref>。这很有可能是12月14日选举人投票前最后一次的重要法律行动<ref name=cnn3>{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/11/politics/election-texas-trump-states-supreme-court/index.html|title=What's next in the states' fight over the election at the Supreme Court|first=Ariane de Vogue and Dan Berman|last=CNN|website=CNN|access-date= 2020-12-11|archive-date= 2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212000854/https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/11/politics/election-texas-trump-states-supreme-court/index.html|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

